        Flood Overlays and Flood Mapping in Brisbane: What Sellers Must Know and Disclose
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Brisbane City Council flood overlays affect thousands of inner-east properties. Here is what the maps mean, what sellers are legally required to disclose, and how to present a flood-affected or flood-adjacent property honestly and effectively.
      </p>
